[{"conversations": [{"content": "──3年前────志願兵面試會場──", "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "初、初次見面。……我、我叫……諾艾兒。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "那個……請、請多……多、指教。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我是維克多。那麼，妳就先說明來面試傳令兵的理由吧。", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "將軍維克多", "speakerName": "名牌", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "那、那個…………因為、我想傳達。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "想傳達，是什麼意思？", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我，那個……呃……書、用書……傳達心情。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "………………………………", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "對、對不起。我﹑我……不太擅長、說話。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "不擅長說話嗎，即使如此妳還是來到了這裡……", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……嗯。", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "別在意。繼續吧。", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……（點頭）", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "小、小時候……讀過的書上寫著，不管是言語……還是、書信。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "什、什麼形式，都沒關係。只要能傳達、心情的話……就可以。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我從書中……學到了、這個。所、所以，我、我也……", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "也、也許……我也可以，傳達給……某個人。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "原來如此……傳令兵需要體力跟速度，妳對自己的體能有自信嗎？", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……沒、沒有。我沒辦法……跑得、那麼快。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "但是……我會努力、跑的！為、為了能早點傳達到！", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "這樣啊。那麼……從現在開始，妳用「是」或「不是」來回答我就好。", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……好、好的。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "傳令兵的任務並不只在國內，有時候必須到其他國家，甚至是前往敵國。", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……是。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "有些命令還得送到危險的地方去，不是想像中那麼輕鬆的任務。這些妳都理解了嗎？", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……是。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "即使如此妳還是報名了……也就是說，對妳而言，傳達訊息的意義就是這麼重大？", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "是、是的！", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……我知道了。之後會通知妳結果，今天的面試就到這裡。", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……是。謝、謝您。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "目前為止來報名傳令兵的人，不是對速度就是對體力自豪，她真是一個特例。", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "不但跑得慢，體力也不行。再加上不擅長說話……", "speakerName": "教官", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "沒辦法把命令書託付給那樣的傳令兵。", "speakerName": "教官", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "而且到底是要怎麼想，才會覺得自己能勝任傳令兵的，真是無法理解──", "speakerName": "教官", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "如果只是將命令書送達，那讓郵差來做就行了。", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "但所謂的傳令兵，就務必將訊息確實地傳達給對方。「有敵人所以逃跑了」的話就困擾了。", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "作為傳令兵，就必須要有不論遭遇任何困難，都會將命令傳達給對方的熱情及專業意識。", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "閣下是指，那位少女有這樣的資質……？", "speakerName": "教官", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "體力和技術可以用訓練彌補，但是，內心卻無法如此。我想看看她未來會如何成長。", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……明白了。", "speakerName": "教官", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "閣下您都這麼說了，那我便發出合格通知，讓她可以開始受訓。", "speakerName": "教官", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "呵……那位少女會如何蛻變，你就好好看著吧。", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "……唉。要正確無誤地傳達命令真的好難。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "因為沒辦法好好地說出來，今天又都是寫在信上了……", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "果然我還是……不適合……當傳令兵嗎。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "妳看起來很沮喪呢。", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "閣、閣下！？", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "在訓練中不斷失敗也沒關係。別在意周圍的評價。", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "只靠言語傳達也不一定是最好的方法。", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "有空煩惱的話，不如去努力達成指示。", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "是……是的，我知道了！", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "…………（偷看）", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……是諾艾兒嗎？", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……！……是、是的。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "進來吧。", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "打……打擾、了。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "妳收到任命通知了吧。", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……（點頭點頭）", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "訓練結束了。之後妳就是我的直屬部下，負責傳令兵的任務。", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……是、是的！", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "在那之後，我作為閣下的傳令兵，在國內奔走──", "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "有時也會潛入敵國，前往夥伴的根據地。", "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "雖然還是不太擅長說話，也遇到很多挫折，但過著充實的每一天。", "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……直到那一天為止。", "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "諾艾兒。從今天起，解除妳直屬於維克多將軍的職務。", "speakerName": "參謀", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……！這、這是……為什麼呢！？", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "維克多將軍……不，維克多已經捨棄一切，離開了這個國家。", "speakerName": "參謀", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "新的所屬單位會再另行通知，在那之前就先待命，以上。", "speakerName": "參謀", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "請、請……等一下！為什麼閣下會離開國家！！", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "區區傳令兵別問那麼多！退下！！", "speakerName": "參謀", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "不知道是不是下達了封口令，完全無法得知關於閣下的情報。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "閣下離開了國家是事實，但是，一定有什麼理由。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "一如往常繼續執行傳令兵任務的同時，也要為了閣下收集情報。我是這麼想的。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}]}, {"conversations": [{"content": "根據收到的指示，是要在這裡領取命令書……", "speakerName": "士官", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "…………（偷看）", "speakerName": "？？？", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "先在這邊等等看好了。傳令兵應該會照預定前來會合──", "speakerName": "士官", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……那個。", "speakerName": "？？？", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "唔哇！？", "speakerName": "士官", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "這個是……來自司令部的命令書。", "speakerName": "？？？", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "妳、妳是……傳令兵嗎？", "speakerName": "士官", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "…………（點頭）", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "真是的，嚇死我了。", "speakerName": "士官", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……算了。命令書我確實如期收到了。", "speakerName": "士官", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "…………（點頭）", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "除了命令書，司令部還有其他口信嗎？", "speakerName": "士官", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……！（寫寫）……請看，這個。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "咦？信？為什麼──", "speakerName": "士官", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……告、告辭了！", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "啊﹑喂！？", "speakerName": "士官", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "今天的傳令……也沒能用言語好好說明。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "雖然想要將口信正確地傳達……但是，用說的真的好難。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "真希望有一天，我也能變得像那孩子一樣呢……", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "我成長的地方，是阿爾貝利亞王國所在的大陸北方──北格拉斯迪亞大陸的某個國家。", "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "那時候的我，非常喜歡讀書，是個內向的孩子。", "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "因為不擅長說話，所以即使跟朋友一起玩……", "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "諾艾兒又不講話了。", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "那……那個……", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "想說什麼就好好講出來啊。", "speakerName": "男孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "那個……就、就是……", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "算了。我們到另一邊去玩。", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嗚嗚……", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "當我因為無法好好說話而沮喪的時候，我都會從書架上……", "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "拿起一本名叫「感情的模樣」的書來讀。", "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "書中登場的女孩，並不是從一開始就很擅長說話。", "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "但是，女孩非常樂觀。「如果不擅長說話，　　那就把想說的話寫在信上吧！」", "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "收到信的人們，感受到了女孩溫暖的心情，所有人都變得笑容滿面。", "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "女孩後來面對任何人都不再緊張，也能順利交談，但她仍然──", "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "「用什麼形式都沒有關係，　只要能把心情傳達出去就可以了。」笑著如此說著。", "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我覺得自己被書中的女孩鼓勵了。", "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "然後，我也想變得跟那女孩一樣……", "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我模仿她，將自己的心情寫在信裡。", "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "將無法用言語表達的心情，寄予書信。", "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我、我不太會認字……", "speakerName": "男孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我也是……", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "……一開始並不順利。", "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "但是，透過在信上畫圖，也漸漸能夠傳達想跟朋友說的事了。", "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "能夠表達自己的心情，這件事對我而言變成了希望。", "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我開始憧憬，有一天自己也能變成不論什麼事都能清晰傳達的女孩子。", "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……現在也還是只依賴著書信，還沒能變得像那個女孩一樣。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "但是，為了能跟她一樣充滿自信地傳達，我得繼續努力呢。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "唔，下一個傳令是──", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}]}, {"conversations": [{"content": "諾艾兒。現在特命妳去調查維克多將軍閣下。", "speakerName": "參謀", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……！？", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "閣下他捨棄一切離開國家的說法，只是表面上的情報。", "speakerName": "參謀", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "妳知道南格拉斯迪亞大陸最大的國家，阿爾貝利亞王國吧？", "speakerName": "參謀", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "是、是的。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "自從阿爾貝利亞國王自稱皇帝，並將國號改成狄亞內魯帝國之後，國內的狀況一直很不安定。", "speakerName": "參謀", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "而閣下他偽裝成傭兵，潛伏在當地。", "speakerName": "參謀", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……閣、閣下他，為什麼，要這樣做？", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "因為他身負王命，而為了完成那個使命……", "speakerName": "參謀", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "他建立傭兵團並打響了名號，順利龔固了能在帝國內自由行動的地位。", "speakerName": "參謀", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "密探的報告內容是這樣說的，但是──", "speakerName": "參謀", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "昨天，我們收到了閣下率領的傭兵團已經被殲滅的聯絡。", "speakerName": "參謀", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "殲、殲滅……為、為什麼！？", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "詳細情況並不清楚。我們只有收到這項情報。", "speakerName": "參謀", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "…………", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "因為閣下身負王命，所以我們必須去確認這項情報的真偽。", "speakerName": "參謀", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "妳去和帝國內的密探接觸，調查關於閣下的狀況。", "speakerName": "參謀", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……是。我、我明白了。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "──狄亞內魯帝國──", "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "那個……關於「幻狼傭兵團」的、情報……請、告訴我。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "就跟之前報告的內容一樣，但是還沒掌握到被殲滅的理由。", "speakerName": "密探‧男", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "實際去、確認了嗎……？", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我去看了戰場遺跡。那狀況……真的十分慘烈。可以的話我不想再看第二次了啊。", "speakerName": "密探‧男", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "那裡……有閣下的、身影嗎？", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我覺得是沒有，但我也不敢斷言。", "speakerName": "密探‧男", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "就算從那邊逃離了，是不是還活著也很難說……", "speakerName": "密探‧男", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "只是有一個奇妙的傳聞，說是傭兵團被殲滅了，但從那天起，境內就出現了專門狩獵帝國兵的人。", "speakerName": "密探‧男", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "不只是帝國兵，那傢伙似乎連無辜村民都不放過，全部殺害了──", "speakerName": "密探‧男", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "雖然不知道傳聞的真偽，但大家都說是「幻狼團長」還活著，在對帝國復仇。", "speakerName": "密探‧男", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……「幻狼團長」，會是、閣下嗎？", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "這個嘛……誰知道呢。關於「幻狼團長」的詳細情報，都很曖昧不明。", "speakerName": "密探‧男", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "但是帝國兵被襲擊是真有此事。有村子因為井裡被下毒，全村的人因此身亡。", "speakerName": "密探‧男", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "妳可以去找其他人那裡問問看，應該能聽到一些城裡的傳聞。", "speakerName": "密探‧男", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……（點頭）", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "──狄亞內魯帝國────密探藏身處──", "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "這、這是來自司令部的、命令書。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "謝啦。那這份報告書可以麻煩妳轉交給司令部嗎？", "speakerName": "密探‧女", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "好、好的，我知道了。……然後，呃、那個。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "妳想問關於「幻狼傭兵團」的事情吧。", "speakerName": "密探‧女", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "…………（點頭）請、請告訴……我。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "雖然不知道是不是真的，我聽說的傳聞是──", "speakerName": "密探‧女", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "有一個用兜帽遮住臉的男人，連被帝國脅迫提供物資的商人都斬殺……", "speakerName": "密探‧女", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "然後在帝國兵停留的村子放火，如果有人想逃，也會毫不留情砍下去。", "speakerName": "密探‧女", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "連、連村民……都……為什麼，要這樣……", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "唔……可能是因為，如果暴露身分會很麻煩吧？", "speakerName": "密探‧女", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "不過傳聞中「幻狼傭兵團」的殘存者就是「幻狼團長」，和暴露身分應該沒關係吧。", "speakerName": "密探‧女", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "這樣的話，可能是因為滿腔怒火而迷失自我了吧。", "speakerName": "密探‧女", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "何況也有傳聞說他渾身染血，手持白刃在深夜中四處徘徊。", "speakerName": "密探‧女", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……為什麼、會這樣。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "很給人添麻煩對吧。……就算傳聞並非全都是事實。", "speakerName": "密探‧女", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "啊，對了。在東邊城裡的夥伴可能會知道更詳細的傳聞。", "speakerName": "密探‧女", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我、我去、看看。……謝謝妳。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "──狄亞內魯帝國────餐廳──", "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "有人看到過長得像維克多將軍的人喔。", "speakerName": "密探‧老婆婆", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……！？在、在哪裡？請告訴我！", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "不確定是不是本人喔？我也只是聽說而已。", "speakerName": "密探‧老婆婆", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "沒關係！我會、去確認！！", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "是嗎？這樣的話……妳就去迷霧森林深處的聖城看看吧。", "speakerName": "密探‧老婆婆", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "他好像在與帝國敵對的阿爾貝利亞第七王子那裡。", "speakerName": "密探‧老婆婆", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "閣下有可能……在聖城。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "謝、謝謝您。我會回司令部……報告這件事。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "……原來如此。傭兵團被殲滅是事實啊。", "speakerName": "參謀", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "被殲滅的原因和傳聞的真偽，只能詢問閣下本人了嗎……", "speakerName": "參謀", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "諾艾兒。妳說閣下現在人在阿爾貝利亞的第七王子那裡？", "speakerName": "參謀", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……是的。雖然還沒、直接去確認……", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "如果考慮到閣下的使命，應該不會錯吧。", "speakerName": "參謀", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "閣下的……使命？", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "閣下是為了調查阿爾貝利亞王族「龍之血」的秘密才潛入的。", "speakerName": "參謀", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我馬上準備命令書。妳帶著這個去找閣下。", "speakerName": "參謀", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "是、是的！", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "──狄亞內魯帝國────聖城附近的森林──", "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "…………（偷看）", "speakerName": "？？？", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……是諾艾兒啊。別躲了，快出來。", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "（驚嚇）……閣……閣下……", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "別叫我閣下，現在的我只是個傭兵。", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "終於……找到您了。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……妳是追著「幻狼團長」的傳聞過來的嗎。", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "是……是的。一直聽到……無法、接受的傳聞……", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "但是妳好像也不是來確認傳聞真偽的樣子。", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "…………", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "有什麼事……不對，不需要問身為傳令兵的妳這種問題吧。是從母國來的命令吧？", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……（點頭點頭）……請收下。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……哼。「俘虜第七王子後盡速歸國。」……嗎。", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "……命令書……您怎麼……撕掉了……", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……妳回去吧。跟他們說，別對我的做法指手畫腳。", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "第七王子是要俘虜還是殺害，由我來決定。", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……這我可不能當作沒聽到啊。", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……！蘭薩弗……！你怎麼在這裡……", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "因為我聽說聖城附近有生面孔在徘徊，所以就加強了夜間巡邏。", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "耶魯菲莉絲……還有──", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……可以跟我們解釋這是怎麼一回事嗎？維克多。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……閣下！請您快逃！這裡由我來！", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "住手，諾艾兒。妳別動手。在他們面前，不要擺出戰鬥姿態比較安全。", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "閣下阻止了我，並開始說起自己的背景和來到這個國家的目的。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "第七王子知道閣下是間諜以後，也不以為意……", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "他相信了閣下的話，並接納閣下成為他們的夥伴。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "然後我也沒有被問罪……", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "他們只是叫我離開這個國家，就將我釋放了。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}]}, {"conversations": [{"content": "我被釋放後，沒有回到母國，而是留在帝國內──", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "繼續調查關於「幻狼團長」的傳聞。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "閣下是「幻狼傭兵團」的團長。但是，他不是那種會將無辜人民捲入戰鬥之中的人。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "既然這樣，又為什麼會流傳著那樣的傳聞呢……", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "為了弄清楚事情的真相，我開始探聽相關的傳聞。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "聽說了嗎？在村中停留的運輸部隊所發生的事。", "speakerName": "帝國兵A", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "是被戴著兜帽的持劍男子襲擊，導致全隊滅亡的事吧。", "speakerName": "帝國兵B", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嗯。而且好像還在大半夜放火，燒掉了整個村子。", "speakerName": "帝國兵A", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "聽說啊，在隔了一座山頭的山頂，帝國兵的部隊在那全滅了。", "speakerName": "青年A", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "而且從附近村莊被強迫帶路的村民，也一起被岩石砸死了……", "speakerName": "青年B", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "搞什麼啊……想復仇的話，只要砍帝國兵就好了吧。", "speakerName": "青年A", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "話說，那個「幻狼團長」，最一開始也只針對帝國兵吧？", "speakerName": "青年B", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "這麼說好像是耶。而且我也記得我聽說過，他是一個臉上帶傷的劍術高手。", "speakerName": "青年A", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "那、那個……", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嗯……？什麼嘛，是妳啊。司令部有什麼新的命令嗎？", "speakerName": "密探‧男", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……（搖頭搖頭）請告訴我……「幻狼團長」的傳聞。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "還是跟之前一樣。兜帽男子連累無辜村民，持續復仇著。", "speakerName": "密探‧男", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "跟當初「幻狼傭兵團」剛被殲滅時只針對帝國兵部隊的傳聞完全不一樣啊，真是的。", "speakerName": "密探‧男", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……剛被殲滅時的、傳聞……嗎？", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "是啊，最一開始的傳聞，是他還會露出臉和帝國兵一戰呢。", "speakerName": "密探‧男", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "那、那個人……長、長什麼樣子？", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我記得好像說是個臉上帶傷，本領高強的男人。", "speakerName": "密探‧男", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "臉上……帶傷。……呃嗯、那個人，從什麼時候……遮住、臉的……？", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "從什麼時候遮住臉的？被妳這麼一說……", "speakerName": "密探‧男", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "好像有時遮、有時不遮……？", "speakerName": "密探‧男", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "（寫寫）……請看，這個。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "信？我看看……", "speakerName": "密探‧男", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "「聽了許多傳聞後又聽了你那番話，　我終於明白了。」", "speakerName": "密探‧男", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "「傳聞有兩種。一種是，　不加以區分進行復仇的兜帽男子。」", "speakerName": "密探‧男", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "「另一種是，只會與帝國兵戰鬥，　臉上帶傷的男子。」", "speakerName": "密探‧男", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "「對照兩個人的戰鬥方式，　　難以想像是同一人所為。」", "speakerName": "密探‧男", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "「使用殘忍戰鬥方式的傳聞裡，　登場的都是兜帽男子。」", "speakerName": "密探‧男", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "「而只會與帝國兵戰鬥的傳聞裡，　則都是臉傷帶傷的男子。」", "speakerName": "密探‧男", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "「兜帽男子把臉遮住，　而另一位則是直接露臉。」", "speakerName": "密探‧男", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "喂，也就是說……", "speakerName": "密探‧男", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "「幻狼傭兵團」的倖存者有兩個人，然後他們各自用自己的方法和帝國兵戰鬥──", "speakerName": "密探‧男", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……（點頭點頭）", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "原來如此……是我們擅自認為存活下來並進行復仇的，只有一個人……", "speakerName": "密探‧男", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……（點頭）", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "不簡單耶……真虧妳能注意到。", "speakerName": "密探‧男", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "…………（搖頭搖頭）", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "比、比起這件事，我有件事……想拜託你。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "錯誤的傳聞……請、請你、澄清、過來。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "諾艾兒，辛苦妳了。調查維克多將軍閣下的任務就到這邊結束。", "speakerName": "參謀", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "不論本次結果如何……閣下還健在就是不幸中的大幸。", "speakerName": "參謀", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "那個……「幻狼傭兵團」，只剩閣下，一個人、了。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我知道。這樣很難繼續執行王命。", "speakerName": "參謀", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "即使如此，就這樣留著讓帝國內部混亂的主因也不錯。……算了。", "speakerName": "參謀", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "把這份命令書交給閣下吧，是歸國命令。", "speakerName": "參謀", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "是……是的！", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "……您又、把命令書……撕掉了呢。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我不會回去的。……不對，應該說回不去了。", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "不管是母國還是王命，都因為復仇而被我捨棄了。但現在，我卻連復仇都辦不到……", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "失去一切的我，還能有什麼未來呢……", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "閣、閣下您……並沒有，失去一切……", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "因為……等著您、歸來的人，部隊的大家、都在等您！", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "基魯斯緹小姐也在等著您！！所以──", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……諾艾兒，將這把劍和刀交給妳的長官，然後告訴他們：「維克多已經作為復仇者死去了」。", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "傳達完以後，就別再來這裡了。", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……！怎、麼可以……！", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……忘掉一切，重奔自由吧。我……也會這麼做。後會無期，諾艾兒。", "speakerName": "維克多", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "我很想叫住閣下……很想追上去。即使心裡如此想著──", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我卻只能看著閣下的背影，目送他離開。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}]}, {"conversations": [{"content": "──狄亞內魯帝國────森林地帶──", "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "將閣下的口信傳達到後，我繼續在帝國執行任務。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "在帝國內騷動一時的「幻狼傭兵團」相關傳聞，現在已經幾乎聽不到了。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "而關於閣下的行蹤，則是毫無頭緒──", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "……（嚇到）是……是誰、在那裡！？", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嗚……", "speakerName": "男子", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……！？傷、傷勢好嚴重……！你還好嗎！？", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……拜託了。將這個……送、到聖城……", "speakerName": "男子", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "請、請等一下！我是──", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "…………", "speakerName": "男子", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "請、請振作一點！", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "他應該逃到了這附近才對……", "speakerName": "帝國兵", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "那個傷勢一定走不遠。把每個草叢都給我翻過來找！", "speakerName": "帝國隊長", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "是帝國兵！得、得躲起來……！！", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "啊，要轉交的信跟……玩偶。不小心、拿過來了。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……咦，這個玩偶，該不會是……？", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "找到了！在這邊！！", "speakerName": "帝國兵", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "被、被發現了……！？", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "請看，他好像在這裡失去意識了。", "speakerName": "帝國兵", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……原、原來、不是我。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "好奇怪……這傢伙，竟然沒有帶著任何東西！", "speakerName": "帝國兵", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "可能在逃跑途中交給了其他同夥也說不定。擴大搜索範圍！", "speakerName": "帝國隊長", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "絕對不能讓那個情報落到「叛逆王子」的手裡！", "speakerName": "帝國隊長", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "聖城……「叛逆王子」……所以那個人是要將情報送去聖城的傳令兵嗎。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……我知道了，同樣作為傳令兵，你的意志，我一定會送達。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "找到了嗎？", "speakerName": "帝國隊長", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "不，還沒有……但是有個足跡往那個方向去了！", "speakerName": "帝國兵", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "他們比我更熟悉地形，再這樣下去，可能會被追上……", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "…………！？", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……安靜。", "speakerName": "？？？", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……咦？", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "有人在追補妳嗎？", "speakerName": "？？？", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "第、第七王子……", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "咦？是不是在哪見過妳……啊對了，妳是那時候，跟維克多在一起的人對吧。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……（點頭）那個……請收下、這個。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "這封信是……！？為什麼會在妳手上？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我被……託付了。他說希望能、送到聖城。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "這樣啊……沒能趕上嗎。不過，妳幫忙保護了這封信呢。謝謝妳。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "那麼，接下來就換我守護妳了。稍微等我一下。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "第七王子說完那些話後，轉眼間，便將帝國兵全部打倒了。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "之後，我協助了第七王子，將那個人帶回聖城……", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"content": "──聖城──", "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "諾艾兒，謝謝妳。托妳的福，我才能帶他一起回來。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "不、不會……沒有的事。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "他為了獲取帝國準備建造的要塞情報，而潛入了帝國。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我收到他聯絡說已經掌握了情報，所以前往與他會合……", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "但我卻沒有趕上。他明明是賭上性命才得到情報的！", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……這個，是和信一起……託付給我的。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "玩偶……是給孩子的伴手禮吧。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "不、不對！這個不是……伴手禮。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "裡面……有東西。縫線、被拆開了一點。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "這個是……玩偶裡面藏了設計圖！？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "好厲害……居然會有這種藏東西的方法，妳竟然會知道呢。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……一開始摸到它的時候，覺得有點……怪怪的。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "而且傳令兵的話，應該會花心思……把情報藏好。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "原來是這樣啊。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "那、那個……第、第七王子。可、可以問、一個問題嗎？", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嗯，妳問吧。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "閣、閣下……維克多閣下他，現在在、哪裡、呢？", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "對不起。我也不知道他在哪裡。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "…………", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "維克多出去旅行了，為了能夠繼續前進。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "繼續……前進……", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嗯。所以諾艾兒，妳有空可以過來這裡。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "但……但是，閣下……閣下他，叫我……別再來……了。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "維克多叫妳別再來，我想是因為他不想讓諾艾兒妳遇到危險喔。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "如果是我，也會對諾艾兒說一樣的話。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……是、是……這樣嗎？像、像我、這樣的人……", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "對維克多而言，妳是很重要的夥伴喔。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "如果不是很重視諾艾兒，他就不會說出用自己來交換，請我們放過妳了。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "…………", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我不知道維克多會不會再回來這裡，但我們已經約好了會再見面。所以……", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "真……真的，我可以、再來……嗎？", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嗯，隨時歡迎喔。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "再也無法見到閣下了。不可以……再見到他。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我原本是這麼想的，但只要來這裡……", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "所以為了那一天，我要將這像要滿溢出來的心情，全部寫進信裡。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "總有一天……一定能夠傳達到的。因為，我是傳令兵……是人與人……之間的橋樑。", "speakerName": "諾艾兒", "type": "conversation"}]}]